summaries.short: Using their personal style to breathe new life into preserved plants, duos create immersive botanical wonderlands made entirely of dried materials before blossoming into floral fashion designers.
summaries.full: Preserved flowers are forever, and life-sized installations are a florist's best friend. For the final team challenge, duos feature their captains as the centerpiece in immersive botanical wonderlands made entirely of dried materials. Next, the artists turn into floral fashion designers, elevating simple slip dresses with intricate, cohesive floral adornments.

summaries.short: For the ultimate shot at $100,000, the remaining artists create whimsical floral illusions, but only two will go on to compete in the final challenge, where they’ll have to transform a life-sized dollhouse into a jaw-dropping floral feat.
summaries.full: Using beautiful blooms to reignite objects that once cast light, scent, and magic, the remaining artists create whimsical floral illusions, but only two will move on to the final challenge, where they’ll have to transform a life-sized dollhouse into a jaw-dropping floral feat for the ultimate shot at $100,000.

summaries.short: The judges give signature floral arrangements a surprising twist before a color wheel of wonder determines which florists will advance to the semi-finals.
summaries.full: After delivering a series of surprises, the judges give the contestants three minutes to grab as many flowers as they can for the creation of signature floral arrangements - with a serious catch. Next, for a spot in the semi-finals, the florists relinquish their fate to a color wheel of wonder.

summaries.short: The competitors take their artistry to new heights as they hoist massive floral sculptures into the air before the bottom three recreate one of the judges’ arrangements, using only an ultra-blurred photo for reference.
summaries.full: The competitors take their artistry to new heights while hoisting massive floral sculptures into the air, making sure every angle creatively integrates color, contrast, and negative space. Next, the bottom three florists face the tricky task of recreating one of the judges’ arrangements - using only a blurry photo for reference.

summaries.short: A multi-layered group challenge brings stunning vistas to life on massive frames before the losing team designs fabulous floral firework displays.
summaries.full: Perspective is everything as teams sprinkle their floral magic onto massive frames to form a picturesque and layered landscape (or seascape). After tackling this intricate task, one group must design fabulous floral firework displays, using brilliant colors and creative techniques to make their petals pop.
